WEBVTT

00:00:14.725 --> 00:00:18.487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

00:00:18.562 --> 00:00:22.162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:25.437
♪Your "same here" carries
a touch of resolve♪

00:00:25.862 --> 00:00:29.412
♪Pack my bags, we can set off right now♪

00:00:29.637 --> 00:00:33.112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:36.712
♪The journey itself is what
truly matters before the destination♪

00:00:36.787 --> 00:00:40.975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

00:00:41.025 --> 00:00:42.612
♪Connect♪

00:00:42.625 --> 00:00:43.275
♪Let's go!♪

00:00:43.612 --> 00:00:47.137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

00:00:47.237 --> 00:00:50.675
♪Today, no dwelling
on negative emotions♪

00:00:50.750 --> 00:00:53.450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:55.262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

00:00:55.262 --> 00:00:58.199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

00:00:59.075 --> 00:01:02.375
=Love in A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

00:01:02.675 --> 00:01:06.275
=Episode 12=

00:01:14.625 --> 00:01:15.945
Lu is back.

00:01:16.920 --> 00:01:18.920
I was planning to visit you,

00:01:18.920 --> 00:01:20.280
but your dad stopped me.

00:01:20.560 --> 00:01:22.000
So I stayed home.

00:01:22.120 --> 00:01:24.720
He said I just found out I'm pregnant,

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:26.000
and I need to be cautious.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:27.790
Hospitals aren't
the safest place right now.

00:01:30.560 --> 00:01:32.400
Mom, you're pregnant?

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:34.600
We hadn't gotten around to telling you.

00:01:34.680 --> 00:01:36.560
With Lu in the hospital,

00:01:37.400 --> 00:01:39.280
and at my age,

00:01:39.280 --> 00:01:40.840
I have to be extra careful.

00:01:40.840 --> 00:01:43.160
Come on, I'll help your sister upstairs.

00:01:53.440 --> 00:01:54.720
Mom, I'm heading up too.

00:02:10.387 --> 00:02:11.325
So

00:02:12.875 --> 00:02:14.927
there's really nothing we can change?

00:02:15.800 --> 00:02:17.525
Things have already unfolded like this.

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:23.080
Maybe I should just come clean to them.

00:02:28.037 --> 00:02:28.877
You once said

00:02:29.520 --> 00:02:32.600
not everything is simply black or white.

00:02:32.725 --> 00:02:34.845
Sometimes the gray area
holds the answer.

00:02:36.200 --> 00:02:38.080
Let's take it step by step.

00:03:01.725 --> 00:03:02.405
Come in.

00:03:09.675 --> 00:03:10.835
What brings you here?

00:03:10.840 --> 00:03:12.200
Shouldn't you be resting at home?

00:03:12.512 --> 00:03:15.792
I came to check on my debtor,
see if he's actually working.

00:03:41.632 --> 00:03:42.792
Ms. Lu,

00:03:42.792 --> 00:03:44.175
what do you think of this?

00:03:44.612 --> 00:03:45.262
(Lu Group. Part 01 Industry Background
and Key Challenges)

00:03:45.337 --> 00:03:46.400
(Industry Trends)

00:03:47.112 --> 00:03:48.712
I think this still falls far short.

00:03:49.752 --> 00:03:51.152
I heard from my dad

00:03:51.152 --> 00:03:53.420
that the USB security token taken
by the kidnappers can't be recovered.

00:03:53.432 --> 00:03:54.232
It's okay.

00:03:54.472 --> 00:03:55.472
But that one million

00:03:55.472 --> 00:03:57.232
was supposed to be your startup capital.

00:03:57.552 --> 00:03:59.832
One million means nothing
compared to you.

00:04:02.192 --> 00:04:03.992
Then what about your dad's situation?

00:04:04.450 --> 00:04:05.890
It was a deficit to begin with.

00:04:07.212 --> 00:04:09.492
We'll earn it back and cover it later.

00:04:10.512 --> 00:04:11.650
Take a look at this project.

00:04:14.912 --> 00:04:18.072
(Key Challenges)
As long as the roadshow wraps up next month

00:04:18.072 --> 00:04:19.310
and the project gets approved,

00:04:19.472 --> 00:04:22.072
three venture capital firms
will immediately come on board.

00:04:23.550 --> 00:04:24.910
With Lu Group joining as well,

00:04:25.687 --> 00:04:29.647
I'll secure 25 percent
equity plus commission.

00:04:31.137 --> 00:04:35.057
Within six months,
revenue can reach 300 million.

00:04:35.672 --> 00:04:36.592
By then,

00:04:36.835 --> 00:04:38.275
we'll be able to pay everything back.

00:04:38.275 --> 00:04:39.675
That would be wonderful.

00:04:39.962 --> 00:04:41.402
Dear Mr. Ye.

00:04:42.352 --> 00:04:43.552
I'm still working.

00:04:44.352 --> 00:04:45.712
Go home and wait for me, okay?

00:04:51.392 --> 00:04:52.312
Go on.

00:05:00.352 --> 00:05:01.232
Sorry about that.

00:05:04.552 --> 00:05:05.992
(This secretary...)

00:05:05.992 --> 00:05:07.752
(Why does she look so much like Mom?)

00:05:08.712 --> 00:05:10.272
(Like Huang Qingbai.)

00:05:11.032 --> 00:05:12.472
(Could it be...)

00:05:12.472 --> 00:05:14.392
(She's starting again?)

00:05:14.975 --> 00:05:16.087
Thank you, Miss Lu.

00:05:17.552 --> 00:05:18.232
You

00:05:18.912 --> 00:05:20.032
know who I am?

00:05:20.155 --> 00:05:21.275
In Mr. Lu's office,

00:05:21.275 --> 00:05:22.923
there's a photo of you together.

00:05:24.832 --> 00:05:26.832
You're new here?

00:05:26.832 --> 00:05:28.050
Yes, Miss Lu.

00:05:32.200 --> 00:05:32.920
Miss Lu.

00:05:34.352 --> 00:05:35.112
Miss Lu.

00:05:37.032 --> 00:05:38.672
I need to deliver documents to Mr. Ye.

00:05:39.072 --> 00:05:39.672
Oh.

00:05:40.437 --> 00:05:41.037
Go ahead.

00:05:51.192 --> 00:05:51.992
Lu.

00:05:52.512 --> 00:05:55.192
Next time, knock before you come in.

00:05:56.312 --> 00:05:56.992
Dad.

00:05:57.512 --> 00:05:59.512
I just ran into your new secretary.

00:06:00.150 --> 00:06:01.190
Oh, did you?

00:06:12.850 --> 00:06:13.952
What about the previous one?

00:06:16.875 --> 00:06:17.595
What is it?

00:06:17.752 --> 00:06:19.672
Why the sudden interest
in my work today?

00:06:20.112 --> 00:06:21.352
What, then?

00:06:21.352 --> 00:06:23.552
Thinking about coming here to intern?

00:06:24.472 --> 00:06:25.472
Nothing like that.

00:06:25.675 --> 00:06:26.755
I was just asking.

00:06:27.872 --> 00:06:29.792
She just looked familiar to me,

00:06:30.512 --> 00:06:32.112
like Huang Qingbai,

00:06:33.072 --> 00:06:34.512
and a bit like Mom too.

00:06:34.512 --> 00:06:36.312
Oh, that's enough.

00:06:36.672 --> 00:06:38.592
Why are you worrying about that?

00:06:39.272 --> 00:06:39.872
Oh, right.

00:06:39.872 --> 00:06:41.112
Since you're here today,

00:06:41.872 --> 00:06:43.925
have lunch with me.

00:06:44.272 --> 00:06:45.072
Come on.

00:06:45.872 --> 00:06:46.632
No, thanks.

00:06:48.362 --> 00:06:49.642
See you at home later.

00:06:54.672 --> 00:06:55.872
Hey, you...

00:07:05.752 --> 00:07:06.632
Come here.

00:07:24.352 --> 00:07:25.672
Remember this.

00:07:26.232 --> 00:07:29.912
Stay out of sight of my daughter
and my wife from now on.

00:07:31.232 --> 00:07:32.792
Understood, Mr. Lu.

00:07:37.472 --> 00:07:38.512
You wanted to see me?

00:07:39.472 --> 00:07:40.672
You like Ye Man?

00:07:42.112 --> 00:07:42.912
So?

00:07:44.190 --> 00:07:45.592
You're not the only one allowed to.

00:07:46.312 --> 00:07:47.632
Do you know who I am?

00:07:48.872 --> 00:07:49.752
Not interested.

00:07:50.832 --> 00:07:53.312
I'm Ye Man's girlfriend
in the United States.

00:07:53.992 --> 00:07:56.272
We've been together for three years.

00:07:56.272 --> 00:07:58.432
If I'm not mistaken,

00:07:58.432 --> 00:07:59.912
you're his stepsister.

00:08:00.712 --> 00:08:02.032
If you keep this up,

00:08:02.032 --> 00:08:03.752
you'll only end up hurting him.

00:08:06.752 --> 00:08:07.992
That has nothing to do with you.

00:08:09.032 --> 00:08:10.552
You're just his ex.

00:08:12.392 --> 00:08:15.752
If I were only his ex,

00:08:15.752 --> 00:08:19.032
why would he keep me
by his side to help him?

00:08:19.032 --> 00:08:20.672
And why would he hide from me

00:08:20.672 --> 00:08:22.152
that the two of you are together?

00:08:23.192 --> 00:08:25.952
Miss Lu, for Ye Man,

00:08:25.952 --> 00:08:27.472
and for your father as well,

00:08:27.472 --> 00:08:29.112
I advise you

00:08:29.112 --> 00:08:30.712
to put an end to this farce.

00:08:48.650 --> 00:08:50.075
Ms. Lu, are you alright?

00:08:50.075 --> 00:08:51.875
Should I call an ambulance?

00:08:53.632 --> 00:08:54.392
No.

00:08:54.632 --> 00:08:55.672
Go back to work.

00:08:55.672 --> 00:08:57.352
Then I'll get going.

00:09:14.912 --> 00:09:18.312
(If I were only his ex,)

00:09:18.312 --> 00:09:21.312
(why would he keep me
by his side to help him?)

00:09:22.832 --> 00:09:24.232
(Do you even know who I am?)

00:09:24.232 --> 00:09:27.575
(I'm Ye Man's girlfriend
in the United States.)

00:10:02.632 --> 00:10:03.632
It's beautiful.

00:10:47.232 --> 00:10:48.032
Sis.

00:10:50.472 --> 00:10:51.752
Sis, what's wrong?

00:10:54.912 --> 00:10:56.752
Sis!

00:11:01.752 --> 00:11:03.032
Sun.

00:11:07.712 --> 00:11:09.872
Mom passed away from this illness too.

00:11:10.312 --> 00:11:11.592
I couldn't escape it either.

00:11:18.592 --> 00:11:20.192
But I hope

00:11:23.672 --> 00:11:26.112
you can live on, healthy and happy.

00:11:39.825 --> 00:11:44.325
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

00:11:44.550 --> 00:11:48.338
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

00:11:48.513 --> 00:11:52.588
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

00:11:52.588 --> 00:11:56.725
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

00:11:56.850 --> 00:12:00.625
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

00:12:00.625 --> 00:12:04.400
♪I'll learn to stop longing
for what's gone♪

00:12:04.400 --> 00:12:06.675
♪The you in my memories♪

00:12:06.675 --> 00:12:08.688
♪Will fade from clarity♪

00:12:08.688 --> 00:12:14.125
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

00:12:15.688 --> 00:12:21.125
♪Forget you completely♪